---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
const title = "7 Best Platforms for Business English Tutors in 2026 | LearnEnglish.Life";
const description = "Looking for a business English tutor? We've ranked the top 7 platforms based on teacher expertise, business curriculum, and price.";
---
<Base title={title} description={description}>
  <Header />
  <main id="main-content" class="bg-neutral-950 min-h-screen">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="text-sm text-neutral-300 mb-4 flex items-center flex-wrap">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-emerald-400">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">›</span>
      <a href="/compare/" class="hover:text-emerald-400">Comparisons</a>
      <span class="mx-2">›</span>
      <span class="text-neutral-400">Best Business English Tutors</span>
    </nav>
<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <div class="mb-8">
    <span class="text-sm text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Guide · Updated April 2026</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">7 Best Platforms for Business English Tutors</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400">To succeed in the global economy, you need more than just general English. You need the language of business.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-12 mt-12">
    <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Preply</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Preply is our top choice for business English due to its specialized search filters. You can find tutors who have backgrounds in finance, law, marketing, or tech.</p>
      <a href="/reviews/preply/" class="text-emerald-500 hover:underline font-bold">Read Review →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Verbling</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Verbling's rigorous teacher screening means you're getting true professionals. Many Verbling tutors offer structured business English curricula.</p>
      <a href="/reviews/verbling/" class="text-emerald-500 hover:underline font-bold">Read Review →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. Cambly Business</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Cambly offers a dedicated "Business" track with lessons focused on presentations, meetings, and negotiations.</p>
      <a href="/reviews/cambly/" class="text-emerald-500 hover:underline font-bold">Read Review →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">4. iTalki</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">With over 10,000 tutors, iTalki has a massive selection of business English specialists at every price point.</p>
      <a href="/reviews/italki/" class="text-emerald-500 hover:underline font-bold">Read Review →</a>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">5. See Guru</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">See Guru offers a more boutique experience with highly qualified teachers and a focus on professional communication.</p>
      <a href="/reviews/see-guru/" class="text-emerald-500 hover:underline font-bold">Read Review →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
    <!-- See Guru CTA -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/40 to-indigo-900/40 border border-emerald-500/40 rounded-2xl p-8 my-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Try See Guru — 3 Free Lessons, No Card Required</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-emerald-100 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Skip the hunt. Get matched with a certified English tutor and start speaking today. No subscription, no credit card, no strings attached.</p>
      <a href="/go/see-guru/" rel="sponsored nofollow" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl text-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-emerald-500/30 transition-all">
        Start My Free Lesson →
      </a>
      <p class="text-xs text-emerald-200/70 mt-4">Trusted by 50,000+ English learners worldwide.</p>
    </div>

</article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
